00:07:09.640 --> 00:07:17.640
So they'll steal information. Sometimes they'll buy it on the dark web, and they'll start to literally build up a credit history for somebody.

00:07:18.640 --> 00:07:29.640
Over the course of years, they develop a large borrowing capacity. And then when they quote unquote, fund the account, they will borrow that sort of large target amount that they had.

00:07:29.640 --> 00:07:37.640
And then that is when the fraud actually occurs. And so that type of corporatized systemic fraud is a growing problem.

00:07:37.640 --> 00:07:47.640
