So bringing in other experts to speak about these trends, to speak about how data is being used, to speak about these different types of use cases to inspire others around you to start to incorporate data.

00:32:29.640 --> 00:32:34.640
Go to data conferences, setting up training opportunities based on skills gaps.

00:32:35.640 --> 00:32:38.640
So where do you want to improve your skills in the data spectrum?

00:32:38.640 --> 00:32:45.640
And even planning events such as data competitions can be a really nice way to identify top talent.

00:32:46.640 --> 00:32:52.640
And then also encourage others to start to think about how they can apply data to their work.

00:32:53.640 --> 00:32:55.640
These are just some ways maybe you can start thinking of.

